    Your Summoner Brooch is a very powerful item which contains
samples of all raw Elements and allows you to store power in
and draw power from its central jewel. In addition, all Brooches
are magically linked so that guildmembers may communicate with
one another through them.

Commands:
  - brooch:           Lists all Summoners currently playing
  - brooch <message>: Sends <message> to all on-line Summoners
  - broff:            Puts you off-line
  - bron:             Brings you back on-line
  - bremote <emote>:  Emotes <emote> to all on-line Summoners
